p Casey's site was a fun project because I was able to start fresh and use modern web technologies.

p Having run Casey's previous site through usability tests, we determined users did not find the design attractive or trustworthy, weren't even sure of what the site was about, and had a difficult time navigating overall.
p To add to this trouble, the poor navigation caused much of the content to be hidden away rather than supporting Casey's expertise.
