p Casey and I decided on several large changes. First, the amount of content on the site didn't justify the extreme amount of subnavigation. We removed the page for testimonials and instead peppered these quotations in with the content across pages.
p I also used several scrolling tricks with the desktop site to engage and entertain the reader without distracting her from the content.
